long_desc.thetext: When displaying attributes with the MultiSelectionAttributeEditor the height of the control is unbounded. The effect is that form sections easily become unbalanced. In contrast with this Bugzilla's CC attribute editor limits the control's height and therefore has a much improved appearance.
